    "analysis": "Previous step loaded the CSVs and produced a concise summary. Findings: metric.csv (2000 rows) and log.csv (450 rows) are available and cover multiple Sock Shop services (carts, catalogue, front-end, orders, payment, user, and DBs). trace.csv and error_logs.csv are empty. A sample metric row timestamp shown is 2024-01-19 04:16:00+00:00, which lies inside the incident window. Next, we must follow the prescribed workflow: compute global thresholds per component-KPI using the full metric series (not filtered), then extract incident-window data for anomaly detection. No root cause determined yet.",
